<T extends AugmentedAnyModelType>(
  item: T
): Storing<T> => {
  // remove location related stuff

  const { operationName, projectRelativePath, operationRelativePath, ...rest } =
    item;

  // remove referenced model data

  const dataParameterNames = getDataParameterNames(item);
  const restWithoutDataParameters = removeOptionalKeysFromObject(
    rest,
    dataParameterNames as any
  );

  // remove `.xyzCalculated` keys

  const calculatedKeys = Object.keys(restWithoutDataParameters).filter((key) =>
    key.endsWith("Calculated")
  );
  const finalItem = removeOptionalKeysFromObject(
    restWithoutDataParameters,
    calculatedKeys as any
  ) as Storing<T>;

  return finalItem;
}
name: makeStoringItem
description:
Three things need to happen in order to store an item

1) keys that can be inferred from the file path are omitted
2) referenced data is omitted
3) calculated data is omitted
